s.apple.com/us/app/investing-com-stocks-finance/id909998122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Finvesting-com-stocks-finance%2Fid909998122&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVERdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=68706ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/investing-com-stocks-finance/id909998122</a><br />\nAndroid:<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fusionmedia.investing&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.fusionmedia.investing%26hl%3Den_US&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVERdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=53ebeea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fusionmedia.investing&amp;hl=en_US</a><br />\n(歡迎推薦其他)<br />\n<br />\n此post常見術語<br />\n港女：恒指或恒指期貨<br />\n美女：道指或道指期貨 或 標普指數/期貨<br />\n三傻：英國富時100指數、德國DAX指數、法國CAC指數<br />\n低水：恒指期貨點數低於現貨水平<br />\n高水：恒指期貨點數高於現貨水平<br />\n平水：恒指期貨點數與現貨點數相等<br />\n棍升/跌：升跌幅度大於20點<br />\n大棍升/跌：升跌幅度大於50點<br />\n升joy/股joy：升跌幅度大於100點並持續<br />\nDH：Day High 今日最高位<br />\nDL：Day Low 今日最低位<br />\nDT：Day Trade 日內交易（即日鮮）<br />\nTA：Technical Analysis 技術分析<br />\n<br />\n牛熊證<br />\n牛熊證特別要注意事項<br />\n1) 買入前留意收回價(即打靶位)<br />\n2) 發行商逢瑞字頭盡量可免則免，溢價食格升少跌多唔郁倒跌樣樣齊<br />\n3) 開市競價時段可以買賣牛熊，但如果開市價打靶、該交易無效<br />\n4) 收市競價時段唔可以買賣牛熊但大戶可以打牛熊靶<br />\n<br />\n心血少朋友可考慮買免打靶恒指ETF<br />\n優點：免打靶、可長時間坐艇<br />\n缺點：回報率比牛熊證少、長時間坐艇要比坐艇費、有槓桿損耗及食價風險<br />\n牛：7200、7231、7242、7205、7221<br />\n熊：7500、7321、7336、7312、7300、7302<br />\n請自行了解以上ETF的詳細資料、管理費、規模、發行商背景及評估相關的潛在風險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手應盡量避免接觸以下產品<br />\n期權(Option)、孖展(Margin)、或其他融資類的衍生工具<br />\n<br />\n再次提醒各位<br />\n保持理性分析及評估有關風險謹慎入市<br />\n<br />\n好友經濟論 (by 鹽巴):<br />\n正常應該call, 係對經濟有希望，睇好個市<br />\n開put 係對經濟有惡意行為，會有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淡友經濟論 (by 我跌左個一蚊):<br />\n正常應該put，順市場走勢，睇淡個市<br />\n牛油已溶化！<br />\n開call係傻牛行為，會比淡友制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，淡友post非淡友圍爐，歡迎任何好友淡友巴絲討論交流"},{"pid":"ef552a96b29899a417b7b195e4e05679e73865fb","tid":2281942,"uid":382063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"yeah"},{"pid":"49de1a8aafc4676d5b2ed24a68d1e9a29f7a2b4e","tid":2281942,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />post 開7左 sorry"},{"pid":"5f567a13b2051e19a43ee3cddd1905d332d130b3","tid":2281942,"uid":53042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e21e5f1771267e111390c9c4d961ba4026de7","tid":2281942,"uid":94484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"以為奈b開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6704fa293093a5ab662371a5fc256d91e1292897","tid":2281942,"uid":382063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49de1a8aafc4676d5b2ed24a68d1e9a29f7a2b4e","tid":2281942,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />post 開7左 sorry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"no. 啱就好啦<br />\n之前skip都試過啦"},{"pid":"4757b0de743695e57e199c6c6558bc36338d2f37","tid":2281942,"uid":382063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"211e21e5f1771267e111390c9c4d961ba4026de7","tid":2281942,"uid":94484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"以為奈b開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008156a37fbe691b34c015327021029edd5a7808","tid":2281942,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11